rashi.description: Bold, energetic, and action-oriented. Aries natives are natural leaders and initiators.
Practical, dependable, and focused on material comfort. Taurus natives value stability and luxury.
Intellectual, curious, and communicative. Gemini natives are versatile and quick thinkers.
Emotional, nurturing, and protective. Cancer natives are deeply connected to family and home.
Confident, charismatic, and ambitious. Leo natives are natural performers and leaders.
Analytical, detail-oriented, and practical. Virgo natives value organization and perfection.
Balanced, diplomatic, and charming. Libra natives strive for harmony and justice.
Intense, passionate, and transformative. Scorpio natives are mysterious and determined.
Optimistic, adventurous, and philosophical. Sagittarius natives are seekers of knowledge and freedom.
Disciplined, ambitious, and pragmatic. Capricorn natives focus on long-term goals and achievements.
Innovative, humanitarian, and unconventional. Aquarius natives are visionaries and thinkers.
Compassionate, imaginative, and spiritual. Pisces natives are deeply intuitive and artistic.

planets.description: Represents vitality, ego, leadership, and fatherly figures.
planets.nature: Malefic when weak or afflicted; otherwise benefic.

planets.description: Represents emotions, mind, nurturing, and motherly figures.
planets.nature: Benefic unless afflicted or in a waning phase.

planets.description: Represents courage, energy, aggression, and younger siblings.
planets.nature: Malefic, but provides strength and courage when well-placed.

planets.description: Represents intelligence, communication, and analytical skills.
planets.nature: Neutral; takes on the nature of planets it is associated with.

planets.description: Represents wisdom, knowledge, prosperity, and spirituality.
planets.nature: Natural benefic; provides blessings and protection.

planets.description: Represents love, beauty, luxury, and relationships.
planets.nature: Natural benefic; promotes harmony and creativity.

planets.description: Represents discipline, hard work, delays, and karma.
planets.nature: Natural malefic; provides long-term benefits through perseverance.

planets.description: Represents obsession, material desires, and foreign connections.
planets.nature: Natural malefic; creates illusions and material desires.
Natural malefic; promotes spiritual growth and detachment.

houses.name: Lagna (Ascendant) / First House
houses.description: Represents self, personality, physical appearance, and overall life direction.
houses.nature: Kendra (center of strength) and Trikona (triangle of purpose). Influences personal growth, vitality, and leadership.

houses.name: Dhana Bhava / Second House
houses.description: Represents wealth, family, speech, and accumulated assets.
houses.nature: Artha (material prosperity). Governs financial stability, family relations, and value systems.

houses.name: Sahaj Bhava / Third House
houses.description: Represents courage, communication, younger siblings, and short journeys.
houses.nature: Upachaya (house of growth). Encourages self-expression, boldness, and skills development.

houses.name: Sukha Bhava / Fourth House
houses.description: Represents home, mother, inner peace, and emotional stability.
houses.nature: Kendra (pillar of support). Governs inner contentment, familial bonds, and real estate.

houses.name: Putra Bhava / Fifth House
houses.description: Represents creativity, children, education, and romance.
houses.nature: Trikona (triangle of purpose). Encourages creativity, intelligence, and joy in life.

houses.name: Shatru Bhava / Sixth House
houses.description: Represents challenges, enemies, health issues, and debts.
houses.nature: Upachaya (house of growth). Challenges to overcome, fostering discipline and resilience.

houses.name: Yuvati Bhava / Seventh House
houses.nature: Kendra (pillar of support). Reflects harmony, alliances, and cooperative ventures.

houses.name: Mrityu Bhava / Eighth House
houses.description: Represents transformations, longevity, secrets, and occult sciences.
houses.nature: Dusthana (house of hardship). Governs transformation, research, and hidden knowledge.

houses.name: Dharma Bhava / Ninth House
houses.description: Represents spirituality, higher learning, and luck.
houses.nature: Trikona (triangle of purpose). Inspires wisdom, moral values, and divine connection.

houses.name: Karma Bhava / Tenth House
houses.description: Represents career, reputation, and public image.
houses.nature: Kendra (pillar of support) and Upachaya (house of growth). Reflects ambitions, success, and recognition.

houses.name: Labha Bhava / Eleventh House
houses.description: Represents gains, social circles, and aspirations.
houses.nature: Upachaya (house of growth). Governs wealth accumulation, social networks, and goals.

houses.name: Vyaya Bhava / Twelfth House
houses.description: Represents losses, spirituality, isolation, and foreign connections.
houses.nature: Dusthana (house of hardship). Reflects detachment, spiritual evolution, and letting go.

birth_number_significance.description: The number of leadership, independence, and originality.
positive_traits: Natural leaders with confidence and ambition.
Innovative and self-reliant.
Strong willpower and determination.
negative_traits: Can be egoistic and domineering.
Impatience and intolerance for others' opinions.
Difficulty in handling criticism.

destiny_number_significance.description: Destined for leadership and pioneering achievements.
positive_traits: Ability to inspire and motivate others.
Strong focus on personal goals and ambitions.
negative_traits: May prioritize personal success over relationships.
Prone to arrogance and overconfidence.

birth_number_significance.description: The number of harmony, cooperation, and sensitivity.
positive_traits: Empathetic and understanding towards others.
Excellent at mediating and resolving conflicts.
Highly intuitive and emotionally intelligent.
negative_traits: Can be overly sensitive and indecisive.
May become dependent on others for validation.
Prone to mood swings and emotional insecurities.

destiny_number_significance.description: Destined for partnerships, harmony, and balance in life.
positive_traits: Creates harmony in personal and professional relationships.
Skilled at collaboration and teamwork.
negative_traits: May struggle with taking independent decisions.
Tendency to avoid conflicts at the cost of personal needs.

birth_number_significance.description: The number of creativity, communication, and self-expression.
positive_traits: Highly creative with a talent for the arts and expression.
Optimistic and charismatic personality.
Strong communication and social skills.
negative_traits: Can be scattered and unfocused.
Prone to exaggeration and overindulgence.
May struggle with following through on plans.

destiny_number_significance.description: Destined to inspire and express through creativity and communication.
positive_traits: Natural ability to uplift and inspire others.
Success in creative or communication-based professions.
negative_traits: May face challenges in maintaining discipline.
Tendency to avoid serious responsibilities.

birth_number_significance.description: The number of stability, practicality, and hard work.
positive_traits: Disciplined and hardworking with a methodical approach.
Dependable and reliable in all areas of life.
Focused on building strong foundations for the future.
negative_traits: Can be overly rigid and resistant to change.
Prone to workaholism and neglecting personal life.
Tendency to focus excessively on rules and details.

destiny_number_significance.description: Destined to achieve stability and success through discipline and hard work.
positive_traits: Ability to create long-lasting structures and systems.
Strong focus on achieving tangible results.
negative_traits: May struggle with adaptability and flexibility.
Prone to becoming overly conservative or cautious.

birth_number_significance.description: The number of freedom, adventure, and versatility.
positive_traits: Dynamic and adaptable to different situations.
Loves adventure and thrives on change.
Quick-thinking and resourceful.
negative_traits: Prone to restlessness and lack of commitment.
Difficulty in sticking to routines or long-term plans.
May overindulge in pleasures and distractions.

destiny_number_significance.description: Destined to explore, adapt, and embrace change in life.
positive_traits: Success in fields that require versatility and quick decision-making.
Ability to bring excitement and innovation to projects.
negative_traits: May face challenges in achieving stability.
Tendency to avoid responsibilities or long-term commitments.

birth_number_significance.description: The number of love, harmony, and nurturing.
positive_traits: Caring and compassionate towards others.
Strong focus on family and community.
Ability to create beauty and harmony in surroundings.
negative_traits: Can be overly protective or controlling.
Tendency to sacrifice personal needs for others.
May struggle with balancing responsibilities.

destiny_number_significance.description: Destined to bring love, harmony, and service to others.
positive_traits: Success in caregiving or creative professions.
Ability to build nurturing and supportive relationships.
negative_traits: May face challenges in asserting personal boundaries.
Prone to taking on too many responsibilities.

birth_number_significance.description: The number of spirituality, introspection, and analysis.
positive_traits: Highly intuitive and spiritually inclined.
Excellent analytical and problem-solving skills.
Appreciates solitude and deep thinking.
negative_traits: Can be aloof and emotionally detached.
Prone to overthinking and skepticism.
May struggle with practical or material aspects of life.

destiny_number_significance.description: Destined to seek spiritual growth and wisdom through introspection.
positive_traits: Ability to uncover hidden truths and insights.
Success in intellectual or spiritual pursuits.
negative_traits: May face challenges in connecting with others emotionally.
Tendency to become overly isolated or withdrawn.

birth_number_significance.description: The number of power, ambition, and material success.
positive_traits: Strong focus on achieving material and financial goals.
Highly disciplined and organized.
Ability to lead and manage large-scale projects.
negative_traits: Can be overly materialistic and power-hungry.
Prone to stress and workaholism.
May struggle with emotional expression.

destiny_number_significance.description: Destined to achieve success through hard work and ambition.
positive_traits: Ability to create wealth and material stability.
Strong leadership and management skills.
negative_traits: May face challenges with work-life balance.
Tendency to focus on results at the expense of relationships.

birth_number_significance.description: The number of compassion, humanitarianism, and selflessness.
positive_traits: Deeply caring and empathetic towards others.
Natural inclination towards philanthropy and service.
Ability to inspire and uplift those around them.
negative_traits: Can be overly idealistic and impractical.
Prone to emotional burnout from helping others.
Difficulty in setting boundaries.

destiny_number_significance.description: Destined to bring compassion and service to the world.
positive_traits: Success in humanitarian or creative fields.
Ability to bring positive change to society.
negative_traits: May face challenges in balancing personal needs with service.
Tendency to take on too much emotional burden.
